                  <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary px-2">
                    <i class="ri-user-line"></i> Sign up
                  </a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </nav>

        <header class="py-3 border-bottom">
          <div class="container d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-center">
            <a
              href="/"
              class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3 mb-lg-0 me-lg-auto link-body-emphasis text-decoration-none"
            >
              <img
                src="https://takshilainstitute.in/images/1732293272tashila-logo.jpeg"
                height="40"
                alt="Takshila Institute"
              />
            </a>
            <div class="col-12 col-lg-auto mb-3 mb-lg-0 d-flex justify-content-center">
              <button class="btn btn-outline-primary ms-2 position-relative">
                <i class="ri-heart-fill"></i>
                <span
                  class="badge bg-danger position-absolute top-0 start-100 translate-middle rounded-circle"
                  style="z-index: 10;">3</span
                >
              </button>
              <button class="btn btn-outline-primary ms-2 position-relative">
                <i class="ri-shopping-cart-2-fill"></i>
                <span
                  class="badge bg-danger position-absolute top-0 start-100 translate-middle rounded-circle"
                  style="z-index: 10;">1</span
                >
              </button>
              <form role="search" class="ms-2">
                <div class="input-group h-100">
                  <input
                    type="search"
                    class="form-control border-primary"
                    placeholder="Search..."
                    aria-label="Search"
                  />
                  <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" type="submit">
                    <i class="ri-search-line"></i>
                  </button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>
        </header>

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="my-5">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
              <img
                src="https://takshilainstitute.in/images/md_sir%20(1).jpg"
                alt="picture of the managing director"
                class="img-fluid rounded-circle mb-3"
                style="width: 100px; height: 100px; object-fit: cover;"
              />
              <div class="ms-3">
                <h2 class="text-dark">
                  Message from N.K. Gupta <span class="text-muted fs-5">(Managing Director)</span>
                </h2>
                <blockquote class="blockquote bg-primary-subtle text-muted p-3 rounded">
                  <p>"It gives me immense pleasure to welcome you at Takshila Institute."</p>
                </blockquote>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <p class="mb-3" style="text-align: justify;">
                It gives immense pleasure to welcome you at Takshila Institute, which is reckoned
                for grooming trailblazers and tender setters for more than 26 years. Takshila has
                heralded an unprecedented regulation in the coaching industry through transforming
                the lives of students aspiring to get into premium medical and engineering
                institutes across the country and realizing their dreams. Over the years, Takshila
                has become the most preferred choice of parents and students and has become
                synonymous with "credibility", "Transparency", "Trust", and the "Best" in the
                Industry. Now, we have PAN-INDIA Networks of 25 centers in about 10 states.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-3" style="text-align: justify;">
                Every year, numerous students appear in Engineering/Medical Entrance Exams across
                India, with dreams of qualifying and scoring a good rank. While treading this path
                of excellence, it becomes quintessential to enroll in an Institute like Takshila
                which aims at holistic grooming of its students in a meritocratic environment
                through experienced and permanent faculty, teaching with the latest technological
                aids. After all, "Nothing succeeds like success".
              </p>
              <p class="mb-0" style="text-align: justify;">
                In other Achievement, based on our glorious past and excellent track record Takshila
                Institute is empaneled with Delhi Government to conduct free classes for one-year
                program for Medical/Engineer Aspirants who are preparing under “JAI BHIM
                MUKHYAMANTRI PRATIBHA VIKAS YOJANA”. in Delhi.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <section class="bg-primary">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-lg-8 pt-4 my-auto">
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-light mb-4">Download our apps & Start learning now</h3>
                  <div class="input-group mb-4 w-75">
                    <span class="input-group-text">+91</span>
                    <input
                      type="text"
                      class="form-control"
                      placeholder="Enter your mobile number"
                    />
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary">Get Link</button>
                  </div>
                  <a
                    href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neeteasyapp&hl=en"
                    class="btn p-0"
                  >
                    <img
                      src="https://takshilainstitute.in/images/1717249857android-app.png"
                      alt="Icon"
                      class="d-inline-block align-middle"
                    />
                  </a>
                  <a
                    href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neeteasyapp&hl=en"
                    class="btn p-0"
                  >
                    <img
                      src="https://takshilainstitute.in/images/1717249870windows-app.png"
                      alt="Icon"
                      class="d-inline-block align-middle"
                    />
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-lg-4 p-4">
                <img
                  src="https://takshilainstitute.in/images/1733042248takshila-combine-phone-removebg-preview.png"
                  class="img-fluid"
                  alt="cta image"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="container">
          <footer class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-5 py-5 my-5">
            <div class="mb-3">
              <a href="https://takshilainstitute.in">
                <img
                  src="https://takshilainstitute.in/images/1732293272tashila-logo.jpeg"
                  class="img-fluid mb-2"
                  alt="Takshila Institute"
                />
              </a>
              <p class="text-body-secondary">© 2025 Takshila Institute. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col mb-3"></div>

            <div class="col mb-3">
              <h5>Important Links</h5>
